example, 3x + 2y = 5 and 3x + 2y

and 6.

mathematical problems leading
to pairs of linear equations in
two variables. For example,
given coordinates for two pairs
of points, determine whether the
line through the first pair of points

second pair. (Limit solutions to
those that can be addressed by
graphing.)

the corresponding
